          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Photon flux integrated from the threshold to the",
                " end-point energy was obtained from the activities of",
                " the (g,n) reaction products of seven elements with",
                " threshold energy from 8.0 to 10.8 MeV (Au, As, Ir,",
                "  Mn, Sn).",
                "These foils were irradiated with Yb to determine the",
                " absolute flux assuming linear shape of the photon",
                " flux up to the end-point energy (14 MeV)."
              ]
            }
          ],
